{"tid":23331,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"「在地下城尋求邂逅是否搞錯了什麼」劍姬外傳TV動畫17年4月新番放送","createTime":"2016-12-05T01:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T16:13:33.000Z","uid":7307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"544b9d0adf5cef42725a32a836f11d4d2f63a6e9","tid":23331,"uid":7307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T01:03:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkacger.com/archives/32586\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F32586&d=10CjJG2g6dwwFxaVJa0PIZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=21302250\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkacger.com/archives/32586</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【真&middot;女主上線】「在地下城尋求邂逅是否搞錯了什麼」劍姬外傳TV動畫17年4月新番放送！<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n原文授權轉載自ACGdoge<br />\n很多人氣作品都會推出各種外傳，其中代表之一是《天才麻雀少女》，不僅有外傳漫畫而且還改編為TV動畫（阿知賀篇）<br />\n現在日本輕小說也有一些人氣作品會推出外傳，有的作品外傳甚至比本篇故事還要精彩&hellip;(例子就不舉了，怕被人打死)<br />\n之前官方宣布《在地下城尋求邂逅是否搞錯了什麼》將會推出劍姬外傳小說改編的TV動畫，在GA文庫的最新書籍銷售信息中已經透露出這個劍姬外傳改編的TV動畫將會在2017年4月新番播出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/05/090322_9204445390aa15f6138d3e98bcbcddaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F05%2F090322_9204445390aa15f6138d3e98bcbcddaf.jpg&h=058ba80f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大西go go go"},{"pid":"849c3bb3720a133c883a582dc240c2ed74c16946","tid":23331,"uid":20941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T04:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e4d636b5c6152b8f6a9bcc376e93704231506b","tid":23331,"uid":11980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:04:28.000Z","msg":"下年最期待新番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk